==English==

===Etymology===
Borrowed from {{bor|en|la|-}}, from a derivative of {{m|la|pugnax}}, from {{m|la|pugnō||I fight}}, from {{m|la|pugnus||fist}}, from {{etyl|ine-pro|en}} roots.

===Pronunciation===
* {{a|UK}}/{{a|US}} {{IPA|/pʌɡˈneɪ.ʃəs/|lang=en}}
* {{rhymes|eɪʃəs|lang=en}}

===Adjective===
{{en-adj}}

